tivation from the OSS source. Renames cust_id to customer_id. device_info JSON is unpacked in the intermediate layer.\\n\", \"materialization\": \"view\", \"patch_path\": \"televerket://models/staging/_staging.yml\", \"full_path\": \"models/staging/stg__network_service_activations.sql\", \"meta\": \"{}\"}, {\"name\": \"stg__network_incidents\", \"unique_id\": \"model.televerket.stg__network_incidents\", \"database_name\": \"televerket\", \"schema_name\": \"main\", \"table_name\": \"stg__network_incidents\", \"owners\": \"[]\", \"tags\": \"[]\", \"package_name\": \"televerket\", \"description\": \"One row per network incident from the OSS source. Renames inc_id to incident_id and customer_ref to customer_id.\\n\", \"materialization\": \"view\", \"patch_path\": \"televerket://models/staging/_staging.yml\", \"full_path\": \"models/staging/stg__network_incidents.sql\", \"meta\": \"{}\"}, {\"name\": \"stg__catalog_products\", \"unique_id\": \"model.televerket.stg__catalog_products\", \"database_name\": \"televerket\", \"schema_name\": \"main\", \"table_name\": \"stg__catalog_products\", \"owners\": \"[]\", \"tags\": \"[]\", \"package_name\": \"televerket\", \"description\": \"One row per product version from the product catalog. Includes valid_from / valid_to for historical versions.\\n\", \"materialization\": \"view\", \"patch_path\": \"televerket://models/staging/_staging.yml\", \"full_path\": \"models/staging/stg__catalog_products.sql\", \"meta\": \"{}\"}, {\"name\": \"stg__billing_invoices\", \"unique_id\": \"model.televerket.stg__billing_invoices\", \"database_name\": \"televerket\", \"schema_name\": \"main\", \"table_name\": \"stg__billing_invoices\", \"owners\": \"[]\", \"tags\": \"[]\", \"package_name\": \"televerket\", \"description\": \"One row per invoice from the billing source. Renames InvoiceID, converts YYYYMMDD date strings to DATE, and casts amount_eur to decimal.\\n\", \"materialization\": \"view\", \"patch_path\": \"televerket://models/staging/_staging.yml\", \"full_path\": \"models/staging/stg__billing_invoices.sql\", \"meta\": \"{}\"}, {\"name\": \"int__network_incidents_enriched\", \"unique_id\": \"model.televerket.int__network_incidents_enriched\", \"database_name\": \"televerket\", \"schema_name\": \"main\", \"table_name\": \"int__network_incidents_enriched\", \"owners\": \"[]\", \"tags\": \"[\\\"network\\\"]\", \"package_name\": \"televerket\", \"description\": \"One row per network incident, enriched with customer name, account status, and contract status from int__customers_enriched. Unresolved incidents are retained with null resolved_at and resolution_time_minutes.\\n\", \"materialization\": \"table\", \"patch_path\": \"televerket://models/intermediate/_intermediate.yml\", \"full_path\": \"models/intermediate/int__network_incidents_enriched.sql\", \"meta\": \"{}\"}, {\"name\": \"int__billing_invoice_settlement\", \"unique_id\": \"model.televerket.int__billing_invoice_settlement\", \"database_name\": \"televerket\", \"schema_name\": \"main\", \"table_name\": \"int__billing_invoice_settlement\", \"owners\": \"[]\", \"tags\": \"[\\\"billing\\\"]\", \"package_name\": \"televerket\", \"description\": \"One row per invoice, enriched with the first payment received for that invoice. Duplicate payments are deduplicated by taking the earliest paid_on date. Invoices with no payment have null payment columns and is_paid = false.\\n\", \"materialization\": \"table\", \"patch_path\": \"televerket://models/intermediate/_intermediate.yml\", \"full_path\": \"models/intermediate/int__billing_invoice_settlement.sql\", \"meta\": \"{}\"}, {\"name\": \"int__customers_enriched\", \"unique_id\": \"model.televerket.int__customers_enriched\", \"database_name\": \"televerket\", \"schema_name\": \"main\", \"table_name\": \"int__customers_enriched\", \"owners\": \"[]\", \"tags\": \"[\\\"customer\\\"]\", \"package_name\": \"televerket\", \"description\": \"One row per customer, enriched with their latest active contract. Preferences (language, paperless, marketing) are carried through from staging. Customers without any active contract retain null contract columns.\\n\", \"materialization\": \"table\", \"patch_path\": \"televerket://models/intermediate/_intermediate.yml\", \"full_path\": \"models/intermediate/int__customers_enriched.sql\", \"meta\": \"{}\"}, {\"name\": \"int__customers_activations\", \"unique_id\": \"model.televerket.int__customers_activations\", \"database_name\": \"televerket\", \"schema_name\": \"main\", \"table_name\": \"int__customers_activations\", \"owners\": \"[]\", \"tags\": \"[\\\"customer\\\", \\\"network\\\"]\", \"package_name\": \"televerket\", \"description\": \"One row per customer, enriched with their most recent network service activation and unpacked device information from device_info JSON. Customers with multiple activations (upgrades) retain only the latest.\\n\", \"materialization\": \"table\", \"patch_path\": \"televerket://models/intermediate/_intermediate.yml\", \"full_path\": \"models/intermediate/int__customers_activations.sql\", \"meta\": \"{}\"}, {\"name\": \"mart_customer_360\", \"unique_id\": \"model.televerket.mart_customer_360\", \"database_name\": \"televerket\", \"schema_name\": \"main\", \"table_name\": \"mart_customer_360\", \"owners\": \"[]\", \"tags\": \"[]\", \"package_name\": \"televerket\", \"description\": \"\", \"materialization\": \"view\", \"patch_path\": null, \"full_path\": \"models/marts/mart_customer_360.sql\", \"meta\": \"{}\"}]--ELEMENTARY-MACRO-OUTPUT-END--", "name": "JinjaLogInfo", "pid": 80439, "thread": "MainThread", "ts": "2026-05-25T19:48:21.252105Z"}}
